data.description: Nestled in an exclusive Agoura Hills enclave, this custom-built home offers a unique blend of modern amenities and natural charm. Surrounded by hiking trails, it provides a perfect balance between tranquility and adventure. The fully remodeled residence features a spacious driveway, attached garage with extra storage, and a one-of-a-kind backyard with a barbecue-friendly patio.The interior boasts a gourmet kitchen with a BOSCH dishwasher, THERMADOR professional gas stove with heating lamps, a SUB ZERO refrigerator, beautiful granite counters and Italian ceramic tile, adjacent to versatile spaces like a bonus room and a living room with a gas/log fireplace. High ceilings and natural light characterize the entire house. Upstairs, three bedrooms offer distinct views, with the master bedroom featuring a renovated bathroom, walk-out balcony, and floor-to-ceiling glass doors.Additional amenities include double-paned windows throughout the house, custom wood shutters, classic hardwood floors, amazing insulation (which will keep heating/AC bills to a minimum), a new AC / Heater & Ducts (updated a few years ago), a newer tile roof installed eight years ago and your very own Tesla charger in the garage with an updated circuit panel. 28348 Laura La Plante Dr is not just a house; it's a character-filled, sturdy home in a safe neighborhood. Enjoy the Agoura Hills Lifestyle with proximity to nature, parks, shopping, and restaurants. Explore highly acclaimed Las Virgenes schools.
